          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div
                class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mt-0.5"
              >
                <i class="ri-check-line"></i>
              </div>
              <span class="ml-2 text-gray-600">Canalizaciones de datos</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div
                class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mt-0.5"
              >
                <i class="ri-check-line"></i>
              </div>
              <span class="ml-2 text-gray-600">Paneles Looker/Power BI</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div
                class="w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mt-0.5"
